After a fresh checkout of the NVL repository, two extra steps are required to
download required external repositories. Do this by running the following git
commands:

git submodule init
git submodule update

See README for configure and build instructions.

Directories Layout
==================
/src                All Buildable Source
/src/nvl            Node Virtualization Layer
/src/nvl/kitten     Kitten Lightweight Kernel         (git submodule)
/src/nvl/palacios   Palacios Virtual Machine Monitor  (git submodule)
